==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outterm
<hw>Out"term`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An external or
superficial thing; outward manner; superficial remark, etc.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Not to bear cold forms, nor men's <qex>outterms</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>B. Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outthrow</ent>⟦br⟧
